    "asOf": "2009-01-15",
    "date": "2009-01-22T20:10:22Z",
    "text": "10k Run for the Border Act - Amends the Immigration and Nationality Act to increase employer civil fines for: (1) hiring, or recruiting or referring for a fee, an alien that the employer knows is not authorized for employment; and (2) continuing to employ such alien.\n\nSets forth a federal-state (and local) allocation of such additional penalty funds."
